'''''The Naked Prey''''' ni filime yo muri [[Amerika]] yo mu 1965  yakozwe kandi iyobowe na Cornel Wilde, nawe ukina mu mwanya wa mbere. Bashyizwe muri veldt yo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo, imigambi ya firime yibanda kumuyobozi wa safari ugerageza kubaho mubuzima bubi bwa veldt, mugihe agerageza kwirinda urupfu rwatewe nabarwanyi ba [[Afurika|Afrika]] bihorera. Iyinkuru ishingiye kuburambe bw'umushakashatsi [[Amerika|w'umunyamerika]] John Colter . Amashusho yamamaye yinjije abanditsi Clint Johnson na Don Peters mu gihembo cya Akademiki cyiza cyumwimerere .

Iyi filime yerekanwe bwa mbere mu iserukiramuco mpuzamahanga rya sinema rya San Sebastián 1965, nyuma isohoka muri [[Amerika]] ku ya 23 Werurwe 1966. Iyi filime yakozwe ku ngengo yimari itarenga 700.000 $, iyi firime yafatiwe ahantu hose muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo.

== uko yakozwe ==
''The Naked Prey yafatiwe'' amashusho muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afrika]] yepfo.    Amashusho ya firime yari afite impapuro icyenda gusa.   Amazina yatangije iyi filime yaherekejwe n’ibishushanyo byerekanwe n’umuhanzi waho Andrew Motjuoadi. <ref name="Prince Audio" />
